headline: PepsiCo (NasdaqGS:PEP) Launches Exclusive Samii Ryan Fashion Collaboration for Summer 2025
summary: PepsiCo (NasdaqGS:PEP) recently launched an exclusive capsule collection in partnership with streetwear brand Samii Ryan. Over the past month, PepsiCo’s share price rose by 4%, aligning with the generally positive market trend while slightly outperforming the flat movement observed recently. The alliance with Samii Ryan may have provided additional excitement around the company’s brand image. The launch of Thirst Guards, a unique beverage delivery initiative, may also have contributed...

headline: 2 Dividend Stocks to Double Up on Right Now
summary: PepsiCo's stock has tumbled despite it being a Dividend King and making growth-oriented investments.  Hershey is going to have horrible earnings in 2025, but it hasn't stopped growing its business.  Emotions on Wall Street tend to swing like a pendulum, going from far too excited to far too pessimistic.
